{"tid":793252,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"［狗咬狗］中韓兩國游泳運動員發生肢體衝突","createTime":"2018-08-25T09:01:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-25T16:44:32.000Z","uid":30441,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9f67c23c77b759aa0aab50e8842df230753b15c6","tid":793252,"uid":30441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T09:01:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/165925_fda0781e56a3b33a07ca8b80a52203be.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2F165925_fda0781e56a3b33a07ca8b80a52203be.png&h=52847a3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n綜合消息：雅加達亞運會傳出中韓兩國游泳運動員發生肢體衝突的消息。韓國方面稱，泳手金惠珍在23日訓練中與中國選手沈鐸碰撞後爭吵，金惠珍被沈鐸毆打。其後，中國代表團兩度向韓方道歉，但韓國代表團不接受。<br />\n<br />\n據韓媒報道，雅加達亞運會韓國代表團團長金晟祚昨日在記者會上透露，韓國游泳選手金惠珍在訓練中被中國女選手毆打，中方教練團當場向韓方道歉。<br />\n<br />\n金惠珍23日在訓練中與中國選手沈鐸碰撞後發生爭吵，在此過程中金惠珍被沈鐸毆打。當時，二人在同一條泳道訓練時，金惠珍的腳接觸到沈鐸的胸部，後者追上金惠珍並拽其腳腕，在水中朝金惠珍的腹部猛踢了兩腳。<br />\n<br />\n隨後，兩國教練勸阻兩人，中方教練團當場向韓方道歉，回到運動員村後又再度致歉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n韓國代表團今日表示，不接受中方的道歉。就算中國選手道歉了，也要接受嚴厲處罰。韓國代表團稱要正式申訴，控告中國游泳選手的暴力行為。<br />\n<br />\n涉事的中國泳手沈鐸21歲，身高1米81，體重72公斤，江蘇常州人。本屆亞運會，沈鐸出戰了女子4&times;200米自由泳接力預賽，決賽她沒有上場，最終中國隊奪金。"},{"pid":"1c47d724c8c4ea3a552f5eca09f67aca66400c1a","tid":793252,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T09:04:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99c0d2ed351e7693770f84c5b857f48fd1d6ee5a","tid":793252,"uid":70013,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T09:05:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s314.siliconimg.com/kb/content_images/2015/09/15/889228/1442307064_373.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs314.siliconimg.com%2Fkb%2Fcontent_images%2F2015%2F09%2F15%2F889228%2F1442307064_373.png&h=c363b74c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f76370040aaa51f167e34f094f0b055ce71a769a","tid":793252,"uid":20563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T09:30:56.000Z","msg":"禁實啦支那狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2591bbfcac0916a0c70eaa40334fa148c4238c3","tid":793252,"uid":115189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T09:31:20.000Z","msg":"生蕃"},{"pid":"09e9be1c8cfa986feb9d1830504ea0b976c3965f","tid":793252,"uid":19126,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T09:54:42.000Z","msg":"根本係泡俾人打，咩肢體衝突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47fb8ca7b4d80755cb74bd436894e278d4d6c555","tid":793252,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09e9be1c8cfa986feb9d1830504ea0b976c3965f","tid":793252,"uid":19126,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T09:54:42.000Z","msg":"根本係泡俾人打，咩肢體衝突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T10:04:04.000Z","msg":"咩接唔接受道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本兩邊都有肢體衝突<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩邊都應該停賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7f5dbd50fa74a5840e4d737cc41c4f80cab39ae","tid":793252,"uid":202348,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"09e9be1c8cfa986feb9d1830504ea0b976c3965f","tid":793252,"uid":19126,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T09:54:42.000Z","msg":"根本係泡俾人打，咩肢體衝突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T10:13:59.000Z","msg":"兩邊都係生蕃賤種，扮咩無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bcace3c4e12b7559c51d1130777422bf737cb90","tid":793252,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-